The paper discusses the transmission of short packets in wireless systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also mentions the need for ultra-high reliability and low latency, which are topics related to control systems (cs.SY) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper discusses the suboptimal transmission of metadata, which is a topic related to cryptography (cs.CR).
